<p>
The <a href="http://git.thousandparsec.net/gitweb/gitweb.cgi?p=tpserver-cpp.git;a=shortlog;h=rfts">ruleset</a>
is pretty stable and we should have a server or two running in the near future.
Currently it only implements the simple version of the RFTS ruleset, but Tyler
will hopefully be working on adding support for the advanced features in his
"copious amounts of free time". 
</p>
   </li>
