<p>
Over the next couple of months we hope to release the 
<a href="http://git.thousandparsec.net/gitweb/gitweb.cgi?p=tpruledev.git;a=summary">Ruleset Development Environment (RDE)</a>
 into the public. This will hopefully allow people to start developing their
